<h2 id='aboutH2'>Who we are</h2>
<div id='roastHistoryContainer'>
	<p id='aboutP1'>Fulton's roasters was started by Joseph Fulton in Heidelberg, Germany back in 1965. Joseph was a second generation coffee roaster who learned the trade from his great-grandfather, the renowned Eugene Fulton. In 1985, Joseph and his wife, Cynthia, along with their two kids, emigrated to Philadlephia in search of a better life in America. Joseph brought his prized machinery and set up shop in the Francisville neighborhood of Philadlephia, servicing the local workers as they walked down Broad street to work in Center City. 
		<br> <br>
		Since our beginnings, we have focused on roasting the best coffee beans, sourced from local coffee trees to create an exquisite cup of coffee. We have created a full range of roasts, light to dark, to satisfy everyone's palate. We stand by our craftsmanship and guarantee the quality of our product, or half your money back -- GUARANTEED!
	</p>
